BT 0.12 g /F2 12 Tf 231.12 765 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 0.5 w 72 753 m 540 753 l S Q
BT 0.12 g /F2 10 Tf 72 720 Td (Q: How quickly will I see results?) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 704 Td (Most people notice initial changes \(energy, bloating, sleep\) within 5-14 days.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 691 Td (Significant body composition changes typically take 4-8 weeks of consistency.) Tj ET
BT 0.12 g /F2 10 Tf 72 666 Td (Q: Do I need to be perfect?) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 650 Td (No. An 80/20 approach is sustainable long-term. Perfection leads to burnout.) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 637 Td (Consistency over perfection, always.) Tj ET
BT 0.12 g /F2 10 Tf 72 612 Td (Q: Should I consult my doctor?) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 596 Td (Yes, especially if you have diabetes, heart disease, kidney issues, are) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 583 Td (pregnant/nursing, or take medications. This guide is educational, not medical advice.) Tj ET
BT 0.12 g /F2 10 Tf 72 558 Td (Q: Can I combine this with exercise?) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 542 Td (Absolutely. Nutrition and movement work synergistically. Start with diet changes) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F1 9.5 Tf 82 529 Td (first, then add exercise once eating habits are established.) Tj ET
BT 0.12 g /F2 10 Tf 72 504 Td (Q: What if I have food allergies?) Tj ET
